OL,6,FTwo men who allegedly plotted to carry
OL,7,Fout an Islamic State-inspired gun
OL,8,Fattack against the Jewish community
OL,9,Fhave appeared in court.
OL,11,FWalid Saadaoui, 36, of Crankwood Road,
OL,12,FAbram, and Amar Hussein, 50, of no
OL,13,Ffixed abode, are accused of plotting a
OL,14,Fterror attack designed to cause
OL,15,F"multiple fatalities using automatic
OL,16,Fweapons" in North West England,
OL,17,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard.
