OL,6,FThe two men had also intended to
OL,7,Ftarget law enforcement and military as
OL,8,Fpart of the "Isil or Daesh-inspired
OL,9,Fterrorist attack", prosecutors alleged.
OL,11,FBoth are charged with the preparation
OL,12,Fof terrorist acts between December 13
OL,13,F2023 and 9 May 2024.
OL,15,FBilel Saadaoui, 35, of Fairclough
OL,16,FStreet, Hindley, also appeared before
OL,17,Fthe court accused of making
OL,18,Farrangements for Walid Saadaoui ` who
OL,19,Fis his brother ` after his death.
