OL,6,FHe pleaded not guilty to a charge of
OL,7,Ffailing to disclose information about
OL,8,Fan act of terrorism between the same
OL,9,Fdates.
OL,11,FThe defendants appeared separately in
OL,12,Fthe dock, flanked by police officers
OL,13,Fand wearing grey sweatshirts.
OL,15,FHussein, who represented himself and
OL,16,Fhad an interpreter, did not speak to
OL,17,Fconfirm his name, date of birth or
OL,18,Faddress. The other two men spoke only
OL,19,Fto confirm their identities.
