OL,6,FAngelo Saponiere, defending Bilel
OL,7,FSaadaoui, said his client was a
OL,8,F"family man" who had not known of the
OL,9,Falleged plans.
OL,11,FDistrict Judge Louisa Cieciora
OL,12,Fremanded all three men into custody to
OL,13,Fappear at the Old Bailey on May 24.
OL,15,FGMP assistant chief constable Rob
OL,16,FPotts, who holds responsibility for
OL,17,Fcounter terrorism policing in the
OL,18,FNorth West, spoke after the hearing.
