OL,6,F"Today's first court appearance has
OL,7,Foutlined some concerning and
OL,8,Fdistressing details about a suspected
OL,9,Fterrorist plot that we allege was
OL,10,Fbeing planned by suspects from Greater
OL,11,FManchester," he said.
OL,13,F"Firstly, we know how significant the
OL,14,Fimpact of this will be. Particularly
OL,15,Ffor our Jewish community in Greater
OL,16,FManchester and across the country.
