OL,6,F"We have worked closely with the
OL,7,FCommunity Security Trust, community
OL,8,Fgroups and key stakeholders prior to
OL,9,Ftoday's hearing, and we will continue
OL,10,Fto update them and support them
OL,11,Fthroughout the course of this case.
OL,13,F"The wider public will understandably
OL,14,Fbe alarmed too."Our preventative
OL,15,Faction has followed a long-running and
OL,16,Fcarefully-managed investigation.
OL,18,F"We are committed to making sure all
OL,19,Fcommunities are safe, and we do not
OL,20,Fcurrently believe there is any wider
OL,21,Frisk directly connected to this case."
