OL,7,Fdirector of the Community Security
OL,8,FTrust, said: "These are very serious
OL,9,Fallegations of a plan to commit a
OL,10,Fterrorist attack against British Jews
OL,11,Fat a time of record antisemitic hate
OL,12,Fcrime levels.
OL,14,F"This is one of a number of recent and
OL,15,Fongoing cases that demonstrate why the
OL,16,FJewish community needs such extensive
OL,17,Fsecurity measures and why our
OL,18,Fcontinuing partnership with police and
