OL,6,F"CST thanks Greater Manchester Police
OL,7,Fand other agencies for their work in
OL,8,Fthis case, and we will continue to
OL,9,Fwork closely with police to provide
OL,10,Freassurance and protection for the
OL,11,FJewish community.
OL,13,F"We urge everyone in the community to
OL,14,Fcontinue as normal, remain alert and
OL,15,Freport any antisemitism or suspicious
OL,16,Factivity at Jewish locations to CST
OL,17,Fand to the police."
